CSS Selector
--

CSS - Cascading Style Sheets

why css selector ?? sometimes working with complex webpages single attribute may not be able to locate the element
even if we give right id or attribute it may not be able to locate the element.

different ways to locate

tag is optional

tag id			tag#id
tag class		tag.classname
tag attribute   	tag[attribute="value"]
tag class attribute 	tag.classname[attribute="value"]


ctrl-f to search element in inspect
